ghtly away from the back of the neck.  Gaze is forward.</p></li></ul><ul><li><h5>Benefits:</h5><p class='text'>Strengthens the abdomen, hip flexors, and spine.  Stimulates the kidneys, thyroid and prostate glands, and intestines.  Helps relieve stress.  Improves digestion.</p></li></ul></section>        </section>

